{"tid":1469463,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"深藍上司咳到甩肺但都唔肯戴口罩,我可以點做？","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T04:45:28.000Z","uid":230019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b8aee4be1ae4dc6e522bf2dfbff1127d7fb09d0e","tid":1469463,"uid":230019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:55:39.000Z","msg":"個深藍上司星期一嘅時候已經係咁咳<br />\n同日晏就拿SL去咗睇醫生<br />\n係佢拿SL前半個鐘佢先戴戴返個罩<br />\n<br />\n噚日星期二佢懶係勤力咁又返返工<br />\n但咳得仲嚴重咗, 聽佢講電話時都係咁大大聲咁咳<br />\n又起曬痰咁,但噚日同今日都係無戴罩<br />\n宜家嗰個都驚行過去搵佢傾嘢或者交文件俾佢<br />\n<br />\n大家幫幫手諗下，有咩辦法可以令佢識趣戴返個罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好禍害人間<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 個深藍上司係公認嘅扮勤力同無能上司<br />\n呢段時間都係咁大大聲講遊行人士有幾衰對社會造成幾多麻煩, 咩都講到警察啱曬<br />\n同絕大部分同事都麻麻地鍾意佢<br />\n<br />\nSorry第一次開Post，講到一舊舊咁"},{"pid":"6180972e0ddd3c7909c1f69e22271b4a27233951","tid":1469463,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:57:50.000Z","msg":"集體sick leave"},{"pid":"54dc5d4b778725385f95423a21e667bde1337d88","tid":1469463,"uid":146724,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yqXr2VJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyqXr2VJ.jpg&h=3fcf2ec0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54e8599061877d0ff6ddff0b80f07775961a15f0","tid":1469463,"uid":22121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2xBP0H4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2xBP0H4.png&h=2ab419dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同佢講戴口罩先係支持警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c14dc7bb946c04e43a589ab8819ac7ce4c0babca","tid":1469463,"uid":230019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6180972e0ddd3c7909c1f69e22271b4a27233951","tid":1469463,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike"